Morsang - sur - Orge is served by no station of the Paris Métro , RER , or suburban rail network . The_closest station to Morsang - sur - Orge is Savigny - sur - Orge station on Paris RER line . This station is located in the neighboring commune of Savigny - sur - Orge , . ( 1 mile ) from the town center of Morsang - sur - Orge .
